					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Well, the "STA" format reminds me NESticle save state. Yes, it's a 4000h bank as described below:
<br />
<br />0000-1FFF Patterns (CHR-RAM / graphics)
<br />2000-3EFF Nametables (screen tilegrids)
<br />3F00-3F1F Palette RAM
<br />3F20-3FFF Palette RAM mirroring (always &amp; 1Fh)
<br />
<br />That's it, buddy. Now, don't ask me about the STA format. ^_^;;</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><strong>Zepper</strong><br /><a href="http://rocknes.web.fc2.com/" class="postlink"><em>RockNES developer</em></a></div>
