				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I don't save states at the <strong>exact</strong> beginning of scanline 240 - I wait until the current CPU instruction is finished, <em>then</em> I save, storing both the scanline number (always 240, though it may change later) AND the PPU cycle number within that scanline (0-340, usually below 20 or so).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
